hidrd
------------------------------------------
HID report descriptor I/O library and conversion tool

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libhidrd0-0.2.0-1bl1
  libobstack1-1.2.3-1bl2
  libxml2-2.10.4-2

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  libobstack-devel-1.2.3-1bl2
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  libxml2-devel-2.10.4-2
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/DIGImend/hidrd

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/DIGImend/hidrd/archive/refs/tags/0.2.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack hidrd-0.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./hidrd-0.2.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/hidrd-0.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/hidrd-0.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhidrd0-0.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhidrd-devel-0.2.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

